channel.description:
First you all call me a conspiracy nut but i have revealed more things then anyone else. Also alot of my suspious about people that i was unable to prove have become provable over time.
Data Collect: http://www.rscheata.net/ppl/
Main points: runeown releases a nexus script that steals rs accts. Both 'Zymic' and 'pplsuqbawlz' recommend runeown be contrbuted, Both post from the same ip. http://www.rscheata.net/ppl/10.jpg Zymic is one of the original members of Fagex and is banned for keylogging.
http://www.rscheata.net/ppl/2.jpg http://www.rscheata.net/ppl/1.jpg
Suspicious facts: pplsuqbawlz uses a different IP at every site. semaphore posted 3min after pplsuqbawlz today. pplsuqbawlz got his accts back. pplsuqbawlz says he let other people on his accts.
Probability of this happening is very small. For pplsuqballz to be innocent by all accounts it would be very low-probability turn of events. For someone to have access to pplsuqballz accts for over 6 months without pplsuqballz knowing????
